  <section class="tutorial" id="community">
  	<header role = "header">
      <h1>A Community Focused on Change. </h1>
      <h2>Like a Laser.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="intro">
    	<p>
        Have you ever wanted to give a day to cause you care about?  Or, maybe you've got a friend that likes to push themselves and you want to support their passion.  
    	</p>
        <P>
          <span class="callout">Be, Cause</span> is a community focused on making connections that drive change.  We offer a place where you can ask people to support your jog for your local animal shelter, jump rope for text-books or anything you can imagine.  We believe that change starts locally, and a thousand people making local changes can effect change globally.
        </P>
